  <p>You will receive a copy of your request via email.</p>
  <p><br>If there are additional details regarding this order you would like to provide, please email Andy Langhurst (<%= mail_to("Langhurst.1@nd.edu") %>) and Laura Sill (<%= mail_to("Laura.A.Sill.4@nd.edu") %>).</p>
  <div class="alert-actions">
    <%= link_to 'New Order', new_just_say_yes_order_path(), :class => 'btn' %>
  </div>
</div>

<%= render :partial => 'just_say_yes_orders/order', :locals => {:order => @just_say_yes_order} %>